<h2>Welcome to the Google Android Challenge POSIT Sandbox!</h2>
<p>This is the server where all the finds recorded by testers like you during the Google Android Challenge come together.</p>
<p>The first thing to do is take a second to <a href="/sandbox/web/register">register an account</a>. Then you can use the tabs above to see what other people are finding, and view them on a map!</p>
<p>Once you register, you can link your phone with your account here by clicking on the <em>Settings</em> tab.</p>
<p>For more information, see the <a href="http://posit.hfoss.org/">POSIT website</a>.
